## ğŸ¯ Launch Plan

### Phase 1: Soft Launch (Week 1)
1. Create public repository
2. Push v2.0.0 code
3. Announce in small communities
4. Gather initial feedback
5. Fix critical issues

### Phase 2: Public Launch (Week 2)
1. Post on major platforms (HN, Reddit, Twitter)
2. Reach out to security influencers
3. Submit to newsletters
4. Monitor engagement
5. Respond to issues/PRs

### Phase 3: Growth (Ongoing)
1. Regular releases
2. Community building
3. Content creation (tutorials, videos)
4. Conference talks (optional)
5. Case studies

